  "text": "Demographic and injury-related characteristics were obtained from participant screening interviews and medical record reviews. The Mini-International Neuropsychiatric Interview [CITATION_1] was used to rule out bipolar disorder and psychosis and to determine the presence or absence of comorbid substance abuse or dependence prior to the baseline assessment.",
